Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.93,0:02:06.18,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:124930,126180}Before everything,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.18,0:02:09.42,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:126180,129420}I will give it to the aunt because\Nshe taught me how to make it!
