Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.57,0:02:16.66,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:135570,136660}Where's the aunt?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.79,0:02:18.74,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:136790,138740}She went to work already!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.85,0:02:20.00,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:138850,140000}Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.22,0:02:21.33,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:140220,141330}Don't worry!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.42,0:02:23.03,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:141420,143030}We'll ask Lassie to deliver it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.00,0:02:26.90,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:145000,146900}I rely on you, Lassie!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.84,0:02:34.35,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:150840,154350}Sandy, we'll be late!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.35,0:02:36.29,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:154350,156290}Wait! Wait! Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.76,0:02:48.85,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:167760,168850}I apologize for making you wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.19,0:03:23.17,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:201190,203170}Doctor, don't do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.09,0:03:26.43,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:205090,206430}Be patient!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.69,0:03:28.99,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:207690,208990}What is the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.51,0:03:31.96,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:210510,211960}I told you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.22,0:03:34.42,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:212220,214420}I have dealt with your wound now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.56,0:03:37.25,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:214560,217250}It would be bad if I didn't treat it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.70,0:03:40.05,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:217700,220050}If you don't come, your bones may break!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.07,0:03:42.27,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:220070,222270}Eh… Please stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.39,0:03:44.03,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:222390,224030}Take care of yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.32,0:03:45.58,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:224320,225580}The next patient!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.64,0:03:48.02,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:225640,228020}Doctor, my daughter is in bad shape today!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.18,0:03:49.48,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:228180,229480}Doctor, please save her!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.50,0:03:50.54,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:229500,230540}xxx
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.79,0:03:52.73,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:230790,232730}Calm down, what happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.41,0:03:56.15,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:233410,236150}Her temperature suddenly rose!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.29,0:03:57.26,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:236290,237260}Doctor!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.66,0:04:01.00,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:239660,241000}Put her here!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.09,0:04:07.95,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:246090,247950}Doctor, what's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.03,0:04:09.36,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:248030,249360}It's not bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.44,0:04:11.11,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:249440,251110}But it hurts a lot!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.22,0:04:14.40,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:251220,254400}Because parents are upset\Nwhen the child is sick!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.65,0:04:19.65,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:255650,259650}Give her good food, and\Nlet her sleep comfortably.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.80,0:04:20.70,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:259800,260700}But…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.06,0:04:26.89,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:261060,266890}I think your baby feels cold because\Nshe's covered with many blankets, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.97,0:04:27.60,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:266970,267600}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.94,0:04:30.31,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:267940,270310}I understand this feeling.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.46,0:04:32.94,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:270460,272940}You have to let her play a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.24,0:04:34.42,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:273240,274420}Is that just it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.84,0:04:39.54,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:274840,279540}It's important to monitor\Nthe temperature of young children.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.07,0:04:40.68,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:280070,280680}Well…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.90,0:04:44.19,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:280900,284190}Because of what happened\Nto her she feels cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.53,0:04:45.26,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:284530,285260}Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.91,0:04:47.67,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:285910,287670}Be careful!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.67,0:04:51.17,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:287670,291170}Doctor, I still don't want her to move much!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.30,0:04:52.59,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:291300,292590}Foolish!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.72,0:04:55.14,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:292720,295140}What's in your mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.30,0:04:59.07,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:295300,299070}You have to leave this child free!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.72,0:05:04.32,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:303720,304320}Hm!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.35,0:05:07.56,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:304350,307560}This dog steals my popularity.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.92,0:05:10.60,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:309920,310600}Hm!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.79,0:05:13.49,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:311790,313490}- That's it, Doctor!\N- Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.82,0:05:23.57,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:321820,323570}What is the matter? What is the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.94,0:05:27.45,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:325940,327450}Damn…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.45,0:05:29.87,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:327450,329870}Is my face so scary?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.87,0:05:31.79,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:329870,331790}I love kids, but…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.79,0:05:34.67,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:331790,334670}I can't face children!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.90,0:05:37.38,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:334900,337380}Doctor, there are still others!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.65,0:05:50.14,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:348650,350140}Well well!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.80,0:05:53.01,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:351800,353010}Take care of yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.30,0:05:59.59,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:356300,359590}What do you think that\Nyou accompany me today?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.51,0:06:07.88,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:366510,367880}Don't worry!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.32,0:06:10.31,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:368320,370310}She only watches you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.46,0:06:13.43,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:370460,373430}So don't run away, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.69,0:06:22.80,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:381690,382800}What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.04,0:06:24.94,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:384040,384940}Is it delicious?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.99,0:06:25.83,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:384990,385830}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.36,0:06:28.92,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:386360,388920}I wonder if the aunt can taste it?
