Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.98,0:06:35.48,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:391980,395480}I don't mean that, but I mean\Nif it's delicious or not!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.63,0:06:36.94,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:395630,396940}Tasty! Tasty!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.12,0:06:38.79,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:397120,398790}Yes, no doubt about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.74,0:06:44.48,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:403740,404480}Yes!
