Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.85,0:07:07.10,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:424850,427100}It's still unclear.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.20,0:07:10.36,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:427200,430360}But he is the owner of Lassie even grown up, right?
