Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.34,0:07:14.79,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:433340,434790}But definitely….
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.91,0:07:19.32,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:434910,439320}Although he is very angry with it,\Nhe still takes good care of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.70,0:07:23.44,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:440700,443440}By the way, Doctor, why don't you\Ngo somewhere today?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.59,0:07:24.21,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:443590,444210}Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.71,0:07:26.93,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:444710,446930}You have treated many patients today.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.53,0:07:28.88,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:447530,448880}Isn't that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.71,0:07:30.79,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:449710,450790}This is true.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.93,0:07:32.17,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:450930,452170}Well, that may be true.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.25,0:07:35.39,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:452250,455390}I'll go for some time.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.59,0:07:40.05,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:455590,460050}As I have always told you, when anything\Nhappens I can hear the siren of the mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.15,0:07:42.48,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:460150,462480}If something happens, send me a signal.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.76,0:07:44.55,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:462760,464550}What is it today?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.87,0:07:49.15,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:464870,469150}You usually say, "I decided to go today,\NI've been patient enough"!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.30,0:07:51.32,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:469300,471320}Why didn't you say that as usual?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.47,0:07:55.84,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:471470,475840}If the patient is late, I will have\Nto work until evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.18,0:07:59.32,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:476180,479320}You also need to pick up your energy again!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.18,0:08:03.61,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:480180,483610}Well, he began to cast some good words!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.52,0:08:13.28,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:492520,493280}Well…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.64,0:08:15.27,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:493640,495270}Will you go too?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.24,0:08:30.99,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:510240,510990}Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.21,0:08:33.08,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:512210,513080}What is the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.31,0:08:37.70,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:513310,517700}It's true that I asked you to help me, but\NI didn't mean to join me at the fishing too!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.49,0:08:39.81,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:518490,519810}Well it does not matter!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.82,0:08:57.81,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:536820,537810}What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.93,0:09:01.13,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:537930,541130}I'm the only one who knows about this spot!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.17,0:09:15.08,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:554170,555080}Lassie!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.82,0:09:20.08,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:555820,560080}What do you think of\Nthe village of Greenall Bridge?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.94,0:09:23.17,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:560940,563170}I love this village.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.07,0:09:27.54,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:564070,567540}I traveled in many cities and villages
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.54,0:09:29.17,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:567540,569170}but this is a good village.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.17,0:09:31.38,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:569170,571380}Security, peace…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.64,0:09:35.27,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:571640,575270}Also all villagers work hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.13,0:09:45.24,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:580130,585240}Do you think these words come out\Nof an old man only?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.57,0:09:47.01,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:585570,587010}Don't be silly!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.05,0:09:52.12,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:588050,592120}My clinic is a medical clinic.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.67,0:09:56.40,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:593670,596400}Big things are not strange to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.15,0:10:01.49,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:597150,601490}So I have to keep some strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.89,0:10:03.16,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:601890,603160}Do you understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.47,0:10:06.88,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:605470,606880}No, it's not true!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.45,0:10:11.37,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:607450,611370}I have to prepare for those big things!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.17,0:10:18.07,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:613170,618070}I feel like an old man walking around here and\Nthere without paying attention to anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.20,0:10:21.94,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:618200,621940}Nurse Carraclough works alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.48,0:10:25.67,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:622480,625670}If something serious happens there,\Nit will be a big problem!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.00,0:10:30.34,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:628000,630340}If you think about it, I can't sleep at night.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.62,0:10:32.61,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:630620,632610}I didn't even take a nap.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.74,0:10:36.87,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:633740,636870}No, that's not true.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.31,0:10:40.42,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:638310,640420}Although I love my work…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.19,0:10:50.94,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:650190,650940}Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.30,0:10:52.56,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:651300,652560}What's up, Lassie?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.84,0:10:53.53,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:652840,653530}Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.65,0:10:54.89,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:653650,654890}I've got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.42,0:11:00.03,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:658420,660030}Well well!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.24,0:11:02.98,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:662240,662980}Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.85,0:11:04.54,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:663850,664540}Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.99,0:11:12.24,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:670990,672240}What do you think, Lassie?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.65,0:11:14.37,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:672650,674370}Isn't it good?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.06,0:11:26.08,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:683060,686080}I did it badly…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.52,0:11:30.30,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:687520,690300}But Lassie, did you enjoy the day?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.54,0:11:34.47,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:692540,694470}Right! Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.19,0:11:40.49,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:699190,700490}Hm? What is the matter?
Comment: 0,0:12:06.91,0:12:06.91,[chapter],[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:726914,726914}Part B
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.69,0:12:22.73,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:739690,742730}My foot is under the rock…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.29,0:12:40.95,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:757290,760950}I appreciate your concern,\Nbut this is impossible for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.30,0:12:50.08,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:768300,770080}Well, I'll relax.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.26,0:13:08.35,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:787260,788350}Lassie?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.98,0:13:10.27,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:788980,790270}What happened to it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.45,0:13:12.13,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:790450,792130}The most recent thing it did?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.16,0:13:17.00,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:794160,797000}Maybe it is taking a nap at home today!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.37,0:13:29.05,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:805370,809050}It's you, Lassie?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.18,0:13:30.22,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:809180,810220}What is the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.63,0:13:36.74,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:814630,816740}I see that you are in good health, Lassie.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.58,0:13:39.47,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:817580,819470}What are you doing, Lassie?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.04,0:13:43.75,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:823040,823750}Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.46,0:13:51.55,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:830460,831550}Lassie?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.76,0:13:59.05,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:837760,839050}Lassie!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.39,0:14:11.26,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:848390,851260}Where did it go?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.57,0:14:13.20,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:851570,853200}With Sandy's sheep!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.37,0:14:20.64,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:858370,860640}But they're at the farm.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.66,0:14:23.22,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:860660,863220}They didn't came on the pasture today.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.57,0:14:27.47,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:866570,867470}Hm…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.07,0:14:31.34,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:868070,871340}Could it still be with my mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.77,0:14:40.61,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:879770,880610}Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.07,0:14:43.04,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:881070,883040}It's gone for a long time!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.14,0:14:44.98,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:883140,884980}Didn't it came to pick you up?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.25,0:14:47.08,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:885250,887080}But it didn't!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.01,0:14:50.08,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:888010,890080}Where did it go?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.46,0:15:05.70,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:904460,905700}Hello Smarty!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.80,0:15:10.71,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:907800,910710}Smarty, did you see Lassie today?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.93,0:15:25.07,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:923930,925070}Lassie!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.87,0:15:30.70,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:928870,930700}W-what's up, Lassie?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.91,0:15:35.07,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:930910,935070}Just a moment, what are you doing? Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.01,0:15:39.31,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:938010,939310}What's up with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.54,0:15:42.39,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:940540,942390}Today you didn't came to school!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.28,0:15:44.71,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:943280,944710}Where have you been?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.76,0:15:47.33,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:945760,947330}Where were you playing?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.43,0:15:54.99,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:953430,954990}Lassie? What is the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.02,0:15:59.01,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:958020,959010}Ah wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.25,0:16:08.02,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:966250,968020}Wait, Lassie!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.98,0:16:11.17,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:969980,971170}Ah! Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.62,0:16:31.36,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:990620,991360}Ah…!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.92,0:16:33.45,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:991920,993450}Doctor Hopper!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.45,0:16:35.19,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:994450,995190}Oh…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.60,0:16:36.61,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:995600,996610}John!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.82,0:16:39.01,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:997820,999010}Doctor!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.59,0:16:40.83,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:999590,1000830}Doctor Hopper!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.03,0:16:43.45,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1002030,1003450}I wasn't attentive.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.81,0:16:46.62,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1003810,1006620}That's why I fell and the rocks fell\Non my feet, and I can't move.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.17,0:16:56.33,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1013170,1016330}No use, it doesn't move!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.14,0:17:03.08,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1022140,1023080}Lassie!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.17,0:17:06.02,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1023170,1026020}Bring anyone…!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.45,0:17:09.72,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1028450,1029720}I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.00,0:17:20.63,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1038000,1040630}Lassie, I count on you in this!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.97,0:17:22.08,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1040970,1042080}Get anyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.19,0:17:24.25,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1042190,1044250}The first person you meet, brought it here!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.37,0:17:25.33,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1044370,1045330}Did you understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.35,0:17:27.27,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1045350,1047270}The first person you meet!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.34,0:17:41.38,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1059340,1061380}Doctor, are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.86,0:17:45.31,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1061860,1065310}Lassie will attend someone immediately!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.52,0:17:48.47,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1066520,1068470}I'm sorry, John…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.13,0:18:02.02,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1081130,1082020}Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.86,0:18:04.07,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1082860,1084070}It's Lassie!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.69,0:18:08.42,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1086690,1088420}What is the matter? Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.80,0:18:13.15,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1090800,1093150}Well okay, why did you come today?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.55,0:18:14.27,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1093550,1094270}Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.65,0:18:18.47,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1097650,1098470}Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.80,0:18:22.19,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1099800,1102190}My God, what happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.83,0:18:26.20,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1104830,1106200}What's up, Lassie?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.87,0:18:28.62,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1106870,1108620}It's a handkerchief.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.19,0:18:30.59,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1109190,1110590}It's John's handkerchief!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.43,0:18:33.89,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1111430,1113890}SOS! It's bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.63,0:18:46.45,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1125630,1126450}Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.03,0:18:47.99,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1127030,1127990}Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.54,0:18:49.65,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1128540,1129650}What is the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.67,0:18:54.90,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1132670,1134900}John wrote this, he's near the bridge!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.95,0:18:56.44,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1134950,1136440}Don't you know where he is?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.46,0:18:57.52,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1136460,1137520}Does anyone know you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.84,0:18:59.67,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1137840,1139670}xxx
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.59,0:19:01.80,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1140590,1141800}- Oh?\N- Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.24,0:19:14.63,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1152240,1154630}Lassie, are you still looking?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.97,0:19:19.54,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1156970,1159540}How long will we stay like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.88,0:19:20.62,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1159880,1160620}Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.64,0:19:21.82,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1160640,1161820}I'm sorry, John!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.32,0:19:25.60,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1162320,1165600}I've brought you in a difficult situation!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.80,0:19:27.59,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1165800,1167590}Doctor! Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.92,0:19:28.84,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1167920,1168840}Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.35,0:19:33.77,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1169350,1173770}But if Lassie woudn't have told\Nabout my problem…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.93,0:19:36.96,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1173930,1176960}No one wouldn't have found me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.11,0:19:40.99,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1177110,1180990}I would have to wait until someone passed by.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.39,0:19:42.28,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1181390,1182280}Oh…!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.58,0:19:46.81,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1183580,1186810}Thinking about being more patient…!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.41,0:19:49.33,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1187410,1189330}I look like a great man!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.42,0:19:51.09,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1190420,1191090}Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.61,0:19:54.84,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1191610,1194840}John, have you heard that voice just now?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.53,0:19:57.43,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1196530,1197430}Ah…!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.71,0:20:02.68,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1201710,1202680}Lassie!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.07,0:20:05.26,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1204070,1205260}What's up, Lassie?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.64,0:20:06.35,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1205640,1206350}Is it here?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.37,0:20:07.53,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1206370,1207530}Oh, he's there!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.55,0:20:09.15,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1207550,1209150}John! Dr. Hopper!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.82,0:20:11.88,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1209820,1211880}Doctor, the help came!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.04,0:20:14.91,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1212040,1214910}Lassie called my father here!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.18,0:20:16.15,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1215180,1216150}Y-yes…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.72,0:20:20.37,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1218720,1220370}Wait, John!
